Phillip J. POMPEO, Petitioner, v. STATE of Florida, Respondent. William B. SCALDEFERRI, Petitioner, v. STATE of Florida, Respondent. Nos. 45739, 45738. Supreme Court of Florida. Oct. 3, 1974. ADKINS, C. J., and ROBERTS, DEKLE and OVERTON, JJ., concur. ERVIN, J., dissents.
